pageContext.claim: “Now that I am back from Singapore, where we had a great result with respect to North Korea, the thought process must sadly go back to the Witch Hunt, always remembering that there was No Collusion and No Obstruction of the fabricated No Crime.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump continues to falsely say the Democrats colluded with Russian even though it was the victim of the hacking attack used by Russia to influence the election outcome, according to the intelligence community.
